.TH m.nviz.image 1 "" "GRASS 7.8.5" "GRASS GIS User's Manual"
.SH NAME
\fI\fBm.nviz.image\fR\fR  \- Creates a 3D rendering of GIS data.
.br
Renders surfaces (raster data), 2D/3D vector data, and volumes (3D raster data) in 3D.
